      "parameters": {
        "content": "## CAIAC Admin Health v1.0.0\n\n**Trigger:** GET /caiac/health\n**Auth:** HMAC + Bearer token\n**Access:** is_caiac_staff = true only\n\nReturns status of all platform services:\n- Postgres (caiac DB)\n- Qdrant (vector store)\n- Ollama (LLM + embed)\n- Reranker (bge-reranker-v2-m3)\n- HMAC Verifier\n\nAll service checks run sequentially with continueOnFail — a single service outage does not prevent the full health report from returning.",
